<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Uncouple" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Uncouple,</orth> to loose hounds from their couples, to set loose: <cit><quote>u. in the western valley; let them go,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. IV, 1, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>u. here,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 3</bibl></cit>. With <emph>at</emph>: <cit><quote>u. at the timorous flying hare,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 674" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 674</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>